{"tid":273244,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[環團發功] 全港泊位佔地等同70萬間屋　環團斥荒謬","createTime":"2017-06-06T11:47:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-06T23:16:01.000Z","uid":2416,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1e4e05d1be4af3ca75ffb5ab0872d42f5b3e065c","tid":273244,"uid":2416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T11:47:28.000Z","msg":"香港泊車位不足問題嚴重，不少車主及運輸業人士均要求港府增加車位以滿足需求。但環保團體「健康空氣行動」反指，現時全港有超過70萬個泊車位，相當於74萬間一人標準公屋單位(每間約150平方呎)的用地，已用作各種車輛的停車位。數字凸顯出土地錯配的荒謬之處，反映市民的居住及休憩空間需求，比不上汽車的停泊需要。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「健康空氣行動」向立法會提交的意見書指，香港的車輛數目增長驚人，運輸及房屋局如果一日不認真減少泊車位的供應，一日也無法有效減少進入市區的車輛。該組織建議，當局應調高公眾泊位的收費，因目前仍停留在每15分鐘2港元的收費，與市面一般停車場時租20至30港元相比，實在相差太遠，令大量車主寧願繞路尋找收費相宜的泊車位。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n該組織又認為，在美利道公眾停車場拆卸後，當局應在鄰近地區設置泊車轉乘(Park and Ride)設施，鼓勵車主不要將車輛駛進中環地區，改乘其他公共交通工具前往市中心。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10154435232681372&amp;id=133214931371\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D10154435232681372%26id%3D133214931371&d=rLrftLDsJd6NcaqFflm%2Fep7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=fd3ce690\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10154435232681372&amp;id=133214931371</a>"},{"pid":"76840bc71042f3d985b474eace3a0407bfc62153","tid":273244,"uid":57705,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T12:00:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"51376967c6ae4237d754a15e29de45bd95094e70","tid":273244,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T12:10:29.000Z","msg":"弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99dcbf1fc04485460f5eff28e5e3ec8493459279","tid":273244,"uid":2126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T12:29:29.000Z","msg":"冇腦"},{"pid":"72c43f6ead0617b247840380aa218aec7d79890e","tid":273244,"uid":35774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T12:31:01.000Z","msg":"環保撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81c04cfa715571a525d9e1f8df1ef7917c6622bb","tid":273244,"uid":21707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T12:34:05.000Z","msg":"日本買車要有房證車位證先買得<br />\n<br />\n香港咁細應該效法限購/駛"},{"pid":"f77d147054582ed24470af7af030b1909cee8db8","tid":273244,"uid":26168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T12:50:53.000Z","msg":"唔駛講咁多，又係每日150 嘅問題，諗乜撚嘢辦法都無用，直接解決問題徵結啦含家產"},{"pid":"841c728e8fc4f4f6a79f58515ca148a454d80f29","tid":273244,"uid":92743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T12:52:15.000Z","msg":"環你老保<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2116329c2057bff780b7808b07f5612fdb5d9358","tid":273244,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T12:53:01.000Z","msg":"好心香港推行下單車"},{"pid":"b5afdf86120d200c7754a27d34601437beb1ad2a","tid":273244,"uid":116443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T23:16:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 環保署嘅基金就係養埋呢班垃圾"}]}